{"tid":2375180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"豪乳網紅「超兇對決」疑露暈「小粉紅」走光！親自現身回應","createTime":"2021-01-21T23:37:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-22T01:16:17.000Z","uid":147522,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c369c5a7926df2b22f869e24250003bafa51db5f","tid":2375180,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T23:37:09.000Z","msg":"因為一張搭乘捷運的豪乳側拍，讓網紅「泥泥學姐」從素人一夕間成為高度關注對象，近期她更為了個人首本寫真書《泥是唯一：泥泥JANiE寫真書》勤跑宣傳，近日泥泥學姐和知名網紅Joeman合作拍片，不料在預告照片中，竟疑似露暈走光，讓泥泥學姐也親自現身回應！<br />\n<br />\nJoeman在社群平台上透露，於農曆春節將會播出精彩的《Joe是要對決》強檔，以「平價內衣」PK「高單價內衣」，該集來賓包括艾瑞絲、啾啾、泥泥學姐等女神級組合，讓Joeman都直嘆說：「眼神完全不知道要放哪裡的一集&hellip;」讓粉絲相當期待。<br />\n<br />\n然而在預告照中，卻有網友赫然發現，「泥泥學姐」的豪乳前疑似露點，乳暈似乎不小心走光，因此紛紛留言提醒，隨後泥泥學姐也親自回覆「我們都保護的很好啦！是陰影而已～抱歉讓大家失望惹。」<br />\n<br />\n擁有百萬粉絲的泥泥學姐身材十分兇猛，近期因推出寫真集po辣照更是不手軟，不少香豔性感寫真照皆搶先曝光，只見她一排釦子幾乎要爆裂，超猛車頭燈讓粉絲看了感受到莫名的壓迫感！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dXDiM1X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdXDiM1X.jpg&h=5f77c436&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a71b66399edf815abe6d980e6ba1edc93b362e49","tid":2375180,"uid":245819,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T23:45:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mWxSRwn.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmWxSRwn.gif&h=5ceafd04&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d2985f6d1eabf68007bcc883f08cf070a265908c","tid":2375180,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T23:54:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df1d9bc0e6f9b47b8a34bf5a5f15f3b55e3bebb1","tid":2375180,"uid":13504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T23:55:51.000Z","msg":"片呢"},{"pid":"94af9b238c84bf2909597afdb3b0b252374b9464","tid":2375180,"uid":328494,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T00:05:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/147522\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/147522</a><br />\n拉。<br />\n波台狗又開啲無聊topic喺時事台。"},{"pid":"24f54cfebd131939aff5a717e19107037505c9c8","tid":2375180,"uid":147029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T00:05:55.000Z","msg":"Joeman同阿屎好撚似樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e04b68fb048188d63e93702bc901febcab6f10f","tid":2375180,"uid":63017,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T01:16:17.000Z","msg":"唔好洗時事台版"}]}